iv></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"font-serif text-lg font-bold tracking-wide transition-all duration-400 group-hover:tracking-wider text-navy group-hover:text-forest\">Face of Change</span></div></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center space-x-1\"><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2 group\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-out relative z-10 text-navy/70 group-hover:text-navy\">Home</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-navy/[0.04]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.92)\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-[2px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-forest/0 via-forest to-forest/0\" style=\"width:0%;opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50%)\"></div></a><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2 group\" href=\"/about\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-out relative z-10 text-forest\">About Us</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-navy/[0.04]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.92)\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-[2px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-forest/0 via-forest to-forest/0\" style=\"width:70%;opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%)\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-1.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-forest\"></div></a><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2 group\" href=\"/projects\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-out relative z-10 text-navy/70 group-hover:text-navy\">Our Projects</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-navy/[0.04]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.92)\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-[2px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-forest/0 via-forest to-forest/0\" style=\"width:0%;opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50%)\"></div></a><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2 group\" href=\"/impact\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-out relative z-10 text-navy/70 group-hover:text-navy\">Impact</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-navy/[0.04]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.92)\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-[2px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-forest/0 via-forest to-forest/0\" style=\"width:0%;opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50%)\"></div></a><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2 group\" href=\"/media\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-out relative z-10 text-navy/70 group-hover:text-navy\">Media</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-navy/[0.04]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.92)\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-[2px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-forest/0 via-forest to-forest/0\" style=\"width:0%;opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50%)\"></div></a><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2 group\" href=\"/contact\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-out relative z-10 text-navy/70 group-hover:text-navy\">Contact</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-navy/[0.04]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.92)\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-[2px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-forest/0 via-forest to-forest/0\" style=\"width:0%;opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50%)\"></div></a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\"><a class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center space-x-2 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-400 ease-out hover:scale-105 active:scale-[0.98] group/donate relative overflow-hidden bg-forest text-white hover:shadow-[0_6px_24px_rgba(22,101,52,0.3)]\" href=\"/contact\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 -translate-x-full group-hover/donate:translate-x-full transition-transform duration-700 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/25 to-transparent\"></div><span class=\"relative z-10\">Donate Now</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-4 h-4 relative z-10 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover/donate:scale-125 group-hover/donate:animate-pulse fill-white text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg></a><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 active:scale-90 text-navy hover:bg-navy/5\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation menu\" id=\"mobile-menu-toggle\"><div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-grow bg-beige/25\"><div class=\"bg-[#FAF9F5] text-navy pt-36 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden border-b border-navy/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-20 space-y-4\"><nav class=\"flex space-x-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40\"><a class=\"hover:text-forest transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a><span>/</span><span class=\"text-navy\">About Us</span></nav><div class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-forest/5 border border-forest/15 backdrop-blur-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-3.5 h-3.5 text-forest\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold text-forest\">Our Vision &amp; Mission</span></div><h1 class=\"font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-none tracking-wide text-navy\">Who We <span class=\"text-forest\">Are</span></h1><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-sans\">Face of Change is dedicated to driving grassroot changes through sustainable initiatives in education, healthcare, and renewable energy.</p></div></div><section id=\"why-we-exist\" class=\"bg-beige py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-20 items-end\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-4\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-forest uppercase block\">Why We Exist</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight\">We Envision An India Where Every Child Has The Chance To Dream And Achieve.</h2></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-base leading-relaxed\">For generations, lack of basic needs has created barriers for remote communities. We believe that by solving education, healthcare, and energy gaps simultaneously, we trigger permanent, generational transformation.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 relative flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.05)] transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-[52px] left-[calc(100%-20px)] w-[calc(100%-80px)] z-0 pointer-events-none\"><svg class=\"w-full h-8\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 20\"><path d=\"M0,10 Q25,18 50,10 T100,10\" stroke=\"#166534\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,4\" fill=\"none\" class=\"opacity-40\"></path><polygon points=\"98,10 93,7 93,13\" fill=\"#166534\" class=\"opacity-40\"></polygon></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-red-50 text-red-600 border-red-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-alert w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"8\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12.01\" y1=\"16\" y2=\"16\"></line></svg></div><span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-navy/10 group-hover:text-gold/20 transition-colors duration-300\">01</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-navy\">The Problem</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Millions of children and families lack access to quality education, basic healthcare, clean water, and stable electricity in remote villages across India, holding back their human potential.</p></div></div><a class=\"pt-8 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-forest group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/about\"><span>Explore approach</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 relative flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.05)] transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-[52px] left-[calc(100%-20px)] w-[calc(100%-80px)] z-0 pointer-events-none\"><svg class=\"w-full h-8\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 20\"><path d=\"M0,10 Q25,18 50,10 T100,10\" stroke=\"#166534\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,4\" fill=\"none\" class=\"opacity-40\"></path><polygon points=\"98,10 93,7 93,13\" fill=\"#166534\" class=\"opacity-40\"></polygon></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 border-emerald-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-navy/10 group-hover:text-gold/20 transition-colors duration-300\">02</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-navy\">Our Action</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed\">We implement holistic, sustainable projects locally—renovating classrooms, holding medical checkup initiatives, installing solar power plants, and building community-led programs.</p></div></div><a class=\"pt-8 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-forest group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/about\"><span>Explore approach</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 relative flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.05)] transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 border-amber-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-navy/10 group-hover:text-gold/20 transition-colors duration-300\">03</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-navy\">The Impact</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed\">We create a lasting ecosystem that empowers children to dream, supports healthy livelihoods, preserves natural environments, and builds resilient, self-sufficient communities.</p></div></div><a class=\"pt-8 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-forest group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/about\"><span>Explore approach</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"stories\" class=\"bg-beige py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-16 space-y-4\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-forest uppercase block\">Stories of Change</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight\">Real People. Real Impact.</h2><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed\">The true measure of our work lies in the transformed realities of rural families. Here are the voices of those whose lives have changed.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.04)] transition-all duration-500 max-w-4xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12\"><div class=\"md:col-span-5 relative min-h-[300px] md:min-h-full\"><img alt=\"Sunita, beneficiary from Mayurbhanj, Odisha\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 35vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudent_sunita.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4\"><span class=\"bg-navy text-white text-[9px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm flex items-center space-x-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-3 h-3 fill-gold text-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg><span>Education &amp; Energy</span></span></div></div><div class=\"md:col-span-7 p-8 sm:p-12 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-between space-y-8 relative\"><div class=\"absolute top-6 right-8 text-slate-100 pointer-events-none select-none\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote w-24 h-24 stroke-[1px] fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest/10 flex items-center justify-center text-forest\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote w-5 h-5 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg></div><blockquote class=\"text-navy/80 font-serif italic text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed\">“<!-- -->We got electricity for the first time in our village through the solar micro-grid. Now I don&#x27;t have to stop studying when the sun sets. I can prepare for my exams at night and achieve my dreams of becoming a teacher.<!-- -->”</blockquote></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between border-t border-navy/5 pt-6 relative z-10\"><div><cite class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-lg not-italic block\">— <!-- -->Sunita</cite><span class=\"text-xs text-navy/50 font-medium\">Student<!-- -->, <!-- -->Mayurbhanj, Odisha</span></div><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-xs font-bold text-forest uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-gold transition-colors\"><span>Read all stories</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"timeline\" class=\"bg-beige/40 py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-20 space-y-4\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-forest uppercase block\">Future Education Initiatives</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight\">Building The Future</h2><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Our vision is long-term. Here is our structural blueprint to scale educational equity and community sustainability over the next three years.</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"hidden lg:block absolute top-[52px] left-8 right-8 h-[2px] bg-navy/10 z-0\"></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10 relative z-10\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 bg-navy/5 text-navy/70 rounded-full\">2025-26</span><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 border-amber-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-laptop w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 5a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8.526a2 2 0 0 0 .212.897l1.068 2.127a1 1 0 0 1-.9 1.45H3.62a1 1 0 0 1-.9-1.45l1.068-2.127A2 2 0 0 0 4 15.526V7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M20.054 15.987H3.946\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-xl text-navy group-hover:text-forest transition-colors\">Digital Learning Initiative</h3><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed\">Deploying solar-powered tablets, internet hotspots, and offline learning tools to 50 rural classrooms, introducing modern digital literacy early.</p></div></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-navy/5 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold text-forest uppercase tracking-wider group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\"><span>Learn roadmap</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4 ml-1 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 bg-navy/5 text-navy/70 rounded-full\">2026-27</span><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 border-emerald-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M17 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M17 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 17h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 17h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M7 2v2\"></path><rect x=\"4\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect x=\"8\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-xl text-navy group-hover:text-forest transition-colors\">STEM Education Programs</h3><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed\">Building hands-on science and engineering mini-labs in regional centers, training teachers to run activity-based experimental science lessons.</p></div></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-navy/5 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold text-forest uppercase tracking-wider group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\"><span>Learn roadmap</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4 ml-1 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 bg-navy/5 text-navy/70 rounded-full\">2027-28</span><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-sky-50 text-sky-600 border-sky-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-xl text-navy group-hover:text-forest transition-colors\">Rural Library Development</h3><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed\">Setting up community libraries stocked with multilingual literature, reference journals, and group studying facilities open to all.</p></div></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-navy/5 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold text-forest uppercase tracking-wider group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\"><span>Learn roadmap</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4 ml-1 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 text-center max-w-lg mx-auto\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-navy/40 uppercase tracking-widest\">Upcoming vision roadmap | Verified by CSR board</p></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-navy text-white pt-16 pb-8 border-t border-white/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2.5\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest flex items-center justify-center text-white border border-white/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-5 h-5 fill-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"font-serif text-lg font-bold tracking-wide text-white\">Face of Change</span></div></a><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm\">Working towards a better India through education, healthcare, clean energy, and community development. Together, we build sustainable and equitable futures.</p><div class=\"flex space-x-4\"><a href=\"https://facebook.com\" id=\"footer-f